txt.en: Everyone is rescued and accounted for!
The group of Longbeard explorers is in trouble and Prince Ingór wishes for the Zhélruka Clan to come to their aid.

'We thank you, brave [placeholder]. Without your assistance we would certainly be done for. I believe I speak for all of us when I say that we are ready to return to safer dwellings whenever you are!'
